{
  "texts": [
    "However, it should be noted that other measures of sample size are similarly predictive of F 1 -scores.",
    "The total number of relevant entities per training data set correlates very closely with the number of sentences (Pearson r=0.998, P<.001).",
    "This high collinearity makes it inadvisable to fit regression models with both predictors.",
    "We did, however, fit a series of models with EPS and a number of relevant entities as predictors.",
    "In all cases, the results were quite similar to those reported in Table 3."
  ]
}